                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Concurrency",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Consider the impact of this update on concurrent transactions. If the "
